**Answer:** Use the `Entity<V>` directly as an element. GPUI implements `Element` and `IntoElement` traits for `Entity<V>`.

**File:** `/Users/denny/.cargo/registry/src/index.crates.io-1949cf8c6b5b557f/gpui-0.2.1/src/view.rs` (lines 28-79)

